keel.Algorithms.Fuzzy_Rule_Learning.Shared.Fuzzy

Class FuzzySingleton

  • java.lang.Object
    • keel.Algorithms.Fuzzy_Rule_Learning.Shared.Fuzzy.Fuzzy
      • keel.Algorithms.Fuzzy_Rule_Learning.Shared.Fuzzy.FuzzySingleton

  • public class FuzzySingleton
extends Fuzzy

    Represents a singleton fuzzy set. A Fuzzy singleton is a fuzzy set whose support is a single point in U with a membership level of 1.0.

    Since:
    JDK1.4
